{"tid":2195150,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"許家印遊艇特准闖港換班   外籍船員登黃金海岸自由行","createTime":"2020-09-09T03:51:17.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-09T03:58:31.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"31a0659b9e8bbca281710173209aff31f83e7be7","tid":2195150,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-09T03:51:17.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200909/PH7UYRI2N5DDZPCT3ZYTPCCLUI/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200909%2FPH7UYRI2N5DDZPCT3ZYTPCCLUI%2F&d=Yvf7L03l0%2FKFASkGPCPwg4Vo%2BdRg%2Bg8pLLdQ7U%2BHcj8%3D&h=c7a5f8bd\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200909%2FPH7UYRI2N5DDZPCT3ZYTPCCLUI%2F&h=d213012f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200909/PH7UYRI2N5DDZPCT3ZYTPCCLUI/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n許家印遊艇特准闖港換班  <br />\n外籍船員登黃金海岸自由行<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/E9IrlZqk28kgc8UQbBmOLT2nbb4=/3726x2067/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/WG3QJR6ZHVCFTIXXH7V2BCNRVI.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FE9IrlZqk28kgc8UQbBmOLT2nbb4%3D%2F3726x2067%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FWG3QJR6ZHVCFTIXXH7V2BCNRVI.jpg&h=e0d397d5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■周日上午，Event駛入屯門黃金海岸遊艇會泊岸。<br />\n<br />\n【新聞焦點】<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】政府豁免船員檢疫入境，成本港第三波疫情爆發關鍵，當局7月底終「認衰」，禁止客船及在港沒有裝卸貨物的貨船船員換班；但規矩原來並非絕對，一艘由恒大集團主席許家印擁有的遠航遊艇，周日（9月6日）「破例」獲准駛入本港泊岸。入境處解釋，上述遊艇因機件問題而未能離港，船員經14天檢疫後，會盡快乘飛機離港。<br />\n<br />\n記者︰伍雅謙 麥筠瑋<br />\n<br />\n政府7月29日起暫停所有客船及沒有在港處理貨物裝卸的貨船船員換班，近日仍有零星船員確診。昨日確診的六人中，便有一人是烏克蘭海員。<br />\n<br />\n消息指，許家印擁有的遠航遊艇「Event」，上月20日疑「闖關」入境本港，一直。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n記者本周日於遊艇會直擊Event泊岸及人員下船的整個情況，數名下船的外籍人士承認。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n根據船舶追蹤網站Marine Traffic顯示，Event於開曼群島註冊，上月14日曾到帛琉，上月。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/uVqSaHOW2RIpPGKlvUSQjzJmZKs=/1652x1181/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/EGGCHZUYLRE27JP3RD4GXU34RQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FuVqSaHOW2RIpPGKlvUSQjzJmZKs%3D%2F1652x1181%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FEGGCHZUYLRE27JP3RD4GXU34RQ.jpg&h=b2e79bac&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■中國恒大集團董事長許家印（左）擁有的遠航遊艇Event，上月20日疑「闖關」入境本港。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n入境處︰機件故障無法離港<br />\n<br />\n行內人士指出，長期停泊在港的遠航遊艇，大多由中國富豪持有，對於Event獲泊岸。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n《蘋果》向恒大集團查詢，集團覆稱遊艇上全體船員已完成14天檢疫，獲入境許可，惟。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n入境處表示，上月20日接獲通知，一艘遊艇有一名香港居民需要返港，原計劃來香港補給後。。。。<br />\n<br />\n海事處指，上述遊艇曾向處方申報8月20日從外地返港。<br />\n<br />\n衞生署稱，8月20日向上述遊艇的13名人士發出強制檢疫令，由8月20日至9月2日23時59分，但未有回應有否為船員檢測病毒。<br />\n<br />\n網站顯示，Event總長60米，寬3.55米，排水量1,102噸，船上設有直升機停機坪，。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n許家印為中國恒大集團董事長，亦是集團黨委書記及統戰部長。許一度躋身中國首富，。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/DEkqeNsDxIMXYUDeG_0iXdzzRqI=/1979x1319/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/E5AOQKSPZVEMTOZRC5U3UMQORI.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FDEkqeNsDxIMXYUDeG_0iXdzzRqI%3D%2F1979x1319%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FE5AOQKSPZVEMTOZRC5U3UMQORI.jpg&h=3fbd6b5c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n【泊 岸】■Event掛上英國海外領地開曼群島旗，根據船身編號，該船有在港註冊俗稱遊艇牌的遊樂船隻牌照。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/hCR8Nj7RS7ZGdJLUIcT0ul0bBJU=/2278x1772/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/MAOTQQ6E3BDIRPZNIPWJFRBLKM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FhCR8Nj7RS7ZGdJLUIcT0ul0bBJU%3D%2F2278x1772%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FMAOTQQ6E3BDIRPZNIPWJFRBLKM.jpg&h=4d5a1b5b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n【落 船】■本周日下午5時半，船上至少七人帶同行李下船，部份人戴上口罩。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/VoNVF6osxfoqUIh3By8cB6PuVJ0=/2363x1772/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/B5K46R7VZFB5BCONPS7CDSR4NM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FVoNVF6osxfoqUIh3By8cB6PuVJ0%3D%2F2363x1772%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FB5K46R7VZFB5BCONPS7CDSR4NM.jpg&h=d7750292&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n【相 迎】■5時45分，一名外籍船員獨自帶同行李上岸，有人在岸邊迎接。"},{"pid":"239f3af08a961cfd44d6ca6f7021d197e7cee173","tid":2195150,"uid":272652,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-09T03:52:39.000Z","msg":"又黎？"},{"pid":"344df96e91e021e2b33805dd749b0dfcaffed469","tid":2195150,"uid":58630,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-09T03:58:31.000Z","msg":"上月14日曾到帛琉 帛琉係台灣盟友<br />\nMark Esper啱啱都去完<br />\n又會咁啱<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}